msg: First step in making stubs cleaner + more efficient.  Rather than using
individual addParameter()/addFault()/etc calls in each method, statically
build up an array of OperationDescs which contains all the metadata,
and simply reference those in the methods.  This avoids a lot of code
(and object creations for ParameterDescs / QNames / etc) each time
